title: 004_Enas vlakas kai misos (1959) (Greek movie).mp4
description:
Apexthanomai ta Greeklish alla dystyxos den ginetai alios.
O Sothrhs enas agnooymenos naftikos pou eixe skhnothethsei ton pnigmo tou me skopo na eispraksei thn asfaleia zohs, epistrefei sto spiti tou, ena xrono meta ton "thanato" tou. En to metaksy, h gohteftikh gynaika tou Ourania, prokeimenou na ksefortothei ton antra ths kai na eispraksei h idia thn asfaleia, prospathei na peisei ton erotevmeno mazi ths THoma na skotosei ton Sothrh. 004_Enas vlakas kai misos.(1959)
